data.description: Welcome to a stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasting 2,287 sq ft of luxurious living space. This captivating property, built in 2017, sits on an expansive .69-acre triple lot, providing a spacious and private oasis. The meticulously crafted interior features a seamless blend of modern design and comfort, offering an open floor plan with abundant natural light.  The heart of the home is a chef's kitchen with premium appliances, granite countertops, and a large island, perfect for entertaining. The master suite is a sanctuary of relaxation, complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom. Three additional bedrooms and well-appointed bathrooms ensure ample space for family and guests.  The exterior is equally impressive, with manicured landscaping enhancing the curb appeal. The triple lot provides a generous backyard space, ideal for outdoor activities and future expansions. Additionally, a large RV building adds practicality for enthusiasts or those in need of extra storage.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional residence yours. Send in your written contract offer now
